The '''Starbright''' was a hotel on [[Barlok/Legends|Barlok]]. It was located a [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometer]] east of the capital city's center. [[Passel Argente/Legends|Passel Argente]] stayed there in [[27 BBY/Legends|27 BBY]].<ref name="Outbound Flight">[[Outbound Flight (novel)|''Outbound Flight'']]</ref>

